item.title: Hybrid help
item.dc:creator: @Darth_Afro56 Darth_Afro56
item.description:
@Darth_Afro56 wrote:

Right click on the Hybridscape Folder. Click New—> Text Document

Copy and paste this in there:

@echo off title HybridScape Compiler "C:\program files\java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

Go to Dile—> Save as…—> Then type in name: compile.bat

There you have your compile.
